283class FrostwingVrykulSearcher
284{
285public:
286 FrostwingVrykulSearcher(Creature const* source, float range) : _source(source), _range(range) {}
287
288 bool operator()(Unit* unit)
289 {
290 if (!unit->IsAlive())
291 return false;
292
293 switch (unit->GetEntry())
294 {
295 case NPC_YMIRJAR_BATTLE_MAIDEN:
296 case NPC_YMIRJAR_DEATHBRINGER:
297 case NPC_YMIRJAR_FROSTBINDER:
298 case NPC_YMIRJAR_HUNTRESS:
299 case NPC_YMIRJAR_WARLORD:
300 break;
301 default:
302 return false;
303 }
304
305 if (!unit->IsWithinDist(_source, _range, false))
306 return false;
307
308 return true;
309 }
310
311private:
312 Creature const* _source;
313 float _range;
314};
315
316class FrostwingGauntletRespawner
317{
318public:
319 void operator()(Creature* creature)
320 {
321 switch (creature->GetOriginalEntry())
322 {
323 case NPC_YMIRJAR_BATTLE_MAIDEN:
324 case NPC_YMIRJAR_DEATHBRINGER:
325 case NPC_YMIRJAR_FROSTBINDER:
326 case NPC_YMIRJAR_HUNTRESS:
327 case NPC_YMIRJAR_WARLORD:
328 break;
329 case NPC_CROK_SCOURGEBANE:
330 case NPC_CAPTAIN_ARNATH:
331 case NPC_CAPTAIN_BRANDON:
332 case NPC_CAPTAIN_GRONDEL:
333 case NPC_CAPTAIN_RUPERT:
334 creature->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_RESET_EVENT);
335 break;
336 case NPC_SISTER_SVALNA: // she never dies or the event is over
337 creature->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_RESET_EVENT);
338 creature->AI()->EnterEvadeMode();
339 creature->AI()->Reset();
340 return;
341 default:
342 return;
343 }
344
345 if (CreatureData const* data = creature->GetCreatureData())
346 creature->SetPosition(data->posX, data->posY, data->posZ, data->orientation);
347 creature->DespawnOrUnsummon();
348
349 creature->SetRespawnTime(5);
350 }
351};

369class npc_highlord_tirion_fordring_lh : public CreatureScript
370{
371public:
372 npc_highlord_tirion_fordring_lh() : CreatureScript("npc_highlord_tirion_fordring_lh") { }

374 struct npc_highlord_tirion_fordringAI : public ScriptedAI
375 {
376 npc_highlord_tirion_fordringAI(Creature* creature) : ScriptedAI(creature), _instance(creature->GetInstanceScript())
377 {
378 }
379
380 void Reset() override
381 {
382 _events.Reset();
383 _theLichKing.Clear();
384 _bolvarFordragon.Clear();
385 _factionNPC.Clear();
386 _damnedKills = 0;
387 }
388
389 // IMPORTANT NOTE: This is triggered from per-GUID scripts
390 // of The Damned SAI
391 void SetData(uint32 type, uint32 data) override
392 {
393 if (type == DATA_DAMNED_KILLS && data == 1)
394 {
395 if (++_damnedKills == 2)
396 {
397 if (Creature* theLichKing = me->FindNearestCreature(NPC_THE_LICH_KING_LH, 150.0f))
398 {
399 if (Creature* bolvarFordragon = me->FindNearestCreature(NPC_HIGHLORD_BOLVAR_FORDRAGON_LH, 150.0f))
400 {
401 if (Creature* factionNPC = me->FindNearestCreature(_instance->GetData(DATA_TEAMID_IN_INSTANCE) == TEAM_HORDE ? NPC_HIGH_OVERLORD_SAURFANG_DUMMY : NPC_MURADIN_BRONZEBEARD_DUMMY, 50.0f))
402 {
403 me->setActive(true);
404 _theLichKing = theLichKing->GetGUID();
405 theLichKing->setActive(true);
406 _bolvarFordragon = bolvarFordragon->GetGUID();
407 bolvarFordragon->setActive(true);
408 _factionNPC = factionNPC->GetGUID();
409 factionNPC->setActive(true);
410 }
411 }
412 }
413
414 if (!_bolvarFordragon || !_theLichKing || !_factionNPC)
415 return;
416
417 Talk(SAY_TIRION_INTRO_1);
418 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_2, 4000);
419 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_3, 14000);
420 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_4, 18000);
421 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_5, 31000);
422 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LK_INTRO_1, 35000);
423 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_6, 49000);
424 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LK_INTRO_2, 58000);
425 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LK_INTRO_3, 74000);
426 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LK_INTRO_4, 86000); // sound last 21 seconds (five more)
427 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_BOLVAR_INTRO_1, 107000);
428 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LK_INTRO_5, 113000);
429
430 if (_instance->GetData(DATA_TEAMID_IN_INSTANCE) == TEAM_HORDE)
431 {
432 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_1, 125000);
433 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_H_7, 134000);
434 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_2, 144000);
435 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_3, 155000);
436 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_4, 167000);
437 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SAURFANG_RUN, 175000);
438 }
439 else
440 {
441 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MURADIN_INTRO_1, 125000);
442 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MURADIN_INTRO_2, 129000);
443 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MURADIN_INTRO_3, 132000);
444 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_A_7, 141000);
445 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MURADIN_INTRO_4, 149000);
446 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MURADIN_INTRO_5, 156000);
447 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MURADIN_RUN, 162000);
448 }
449 }
450 }
451 }
452
453 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
454 {
455 if (_damnedKills != 2)
456 return;
457
458 _events.Update(diff);
459
460 while (uint32 eventId = _events.ExecuteEvent())
461 {
462 switch (eventId)
463 {
464 case EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_2:
465 me->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_EXCLAMATION);
466 break;
467 case EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_3:
468 Talk(SAY_TIRION_INTRO_2);
469 break;
470 case EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_4:
471 me->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_EXCLAMATION);
472 break;
473 case EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_5:
474 Talk(SAY_TIRION_INTRO_3);
475 break;
476 case EVENT_LK_INTRO_1:
477 me->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_POINT_NO_SHEATHE);
478 if (Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _theLichKing))
479 theLichKing->AI()->Talk(SAY_LK_INTRO_1);
480 break;
481 case EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_6:
482 Talk(SAY_TIRION_INTRO_4);
483 break;
484 case EVENT_LK_INTRO_2:
485 if (Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _theLichKing))
486 theLichKing->AI()->Talk(SAY_LK_INTRO_2);
487 break;
488 case EVENT_LK_INTRO_3:
489 if (Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _theLichKing))
490 theLichKing->AI()->Talk(SAY_LK_INTRO_3);
491 break;
492 case EVENT_LK_INTRO_4:
493 if (Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _theLichKing))
494 theLichKing->AI()->Talk(SAY_LK_INTRO_4);
495 break;
496 case EVENT_BOLVAR_INTRO_1:
497 if (Creature* bolvarFordragon = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _bolvarFordragon))
498 {
499 bolvarFordragon->AI()->Talk(SAY_BOLVAR_INTRO_1);
500 bolvarFordragon->setActive(false);
501 }
502 break;
503 case EVENT_LK_INTRO_5:
504 if (Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _theLichKing))
505 {
506 theLichKing->AI()->Talk(SAY_LK_INTRO_5);
507 theLichKing->setActive(false);
508 }
509 break;
510 case EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_1:
511 if (Creature* saurfang = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
512 saurfang->AI()->Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_1);
513 break;
514 case EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_H_7:
515 Talk(SAY_TIRION_INTRO_H_5);
516 break;
517 case EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_2:
518 if (Creature* saurfang = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
519 saurfang->AI()->Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_2);
520 break;
521 case EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_3:
522 if (Creature* saurfang = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
523 saurfang->AI()->Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_3);
524 break;
525 case EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_4:
526 if (Creature* saurfang = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
527 saurfang->AI()->Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_4);
528 break;
529 case EVENT_MURADIN_RUN:
530 case EVENT_SAURFANG_RUN:
531 if (Creature* factionNPC = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
532 {
533 factionNPC->GetMotionMaster()->MovePath(factionNPC->GetSpawnId() * 10, false);
534 factionNPC->DespawnOrUnsummon(46500);
535 std::list<Creature*> followers;
536 factionNPC->GetCreaturesWithEntryInRange(followers, 30, _instance->GetData(DATA_TEAMID_IN_INSTANCE) == TEAM_HORDE ? NPC_KOR_KRON_GENERAL : NPC_ALLIANCE_COMMANDER);
537 for (Creature* follower : followers)
538 {
539 follower->DespawnOrUnsummon(46500);
540 }
541 }
542 me->setActive(false);
543 _damnedKills = 3;
544 break;
545 case EVENT_MURADIN_INTRO_1:
546 if (Creature* muradin = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
547 muradin->AI()->Talk(SAY_MURADIN_INTRO_1);
548 break;
549 case EVENT_MURADIN_INTRO_2:
550 if (Creature* muradin = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
551 muradin->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_TALK);
552 break;
553 case EVENT_MURADIN_INTRO_3:
554 if (Creature* muradin = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
555 muradin->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_EXCLAMATION);
556 break;
557 case EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_A_7:
558 Talk(SAY_TIRION_INTRO_A_5);
559 break;
560 case EVENT_MURADIN_INTRO_4:
561 if (Creature* muradin = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
562 muradin->AI()->Talk(SAY_MURADIN_INTRO_2);
563 break;
564 case EVENT_MURADIN_INTRO_5:
565 if (Creature* muradin = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
566 muradin->AI()->Talk(SAY_MURADIN_INTRO_3);
567 break;
568 default:
569 break;
570 }
571 }
572 }
573
574 private:
575 EventMap _events;
576 InstanceScript* const _instance;
577 ObjectGuid _theLichKing;
578 ObjectGuid _bolvarFordragon;
579 ObjectGuid _factionNPC;
580 uint16 _damnedKills;
581 };

583 CreatureAI* GetAI(Creature* creature) const override
584 {
585 return GetIcecrownCitadelAI<npc_highlord_tirion_fordringAI>(creature);
586 }

763 _isEventDone = _instance->GetBossState(DATA_SISTER_SVALNA) == DONE;
764 me->setActive(false);
765 _aliveTrash.clear();
766 _currentWPid = 0;
767 _handledWP4 = false;

769 me->CombatStop();
770 me->GetThreatMgr().ClearAllThreat();

780 {
781 SetEscortPaused(false);
782 if (_currentWPid == 4 && !_handledWP4)
783 {
784 _handledWP4 = true;

793 void WaypointReached(uint32 waypointId) override
794 {
795 switch (waypointId)
796 {
797 // pause pathing until trash pack is cleared
798 case 0:
799 Talk(SAY_CROK_COMBAT_WP_0);
800 if (!_aliveTrash.empty())
801 SetEscortPaused(true);
802 break;
803 case 1:
804 Talk(SAY_CROK_COMBAT_WP_1);

807 break;
808 case 2:
809 if (!_aliveTrash.empty())

822 break;

826 void WaypointStart(uint32 waypointId) override
827 {
828 _currentWPid = waypointId;
829 float minY = 0.0f;
830 switch (waypointId)
831 {
832 case 0:
833 minY = 2600.0f;
834 break;
835 case 1:
836 minY = 2550.0f;
837 if (Creature* svalna = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_SISTER_SVALNA)))
838 svalna->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_KILL_CAPTAIN);
839 break;
840 case 2:
841 minY = 2515.0f;
842 if (Creature* svalna = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_SISTER_SVALNA)))
843 svalna->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_KILL_CAPTAIN);
844 break;
845 case 4:
846 minY = 2475.0f;
847 break;
848 default:
849 break;
850 }
851
852 if (minY)
853 {
854 // get all nearby vrykul
855 std::list<Creature*> temp;
856 FrostwingVrykulSearcher check(me, 150.0f);
857 Acore::CreatureListSearcher<FrostwingVrykulSearcher> searcher(me, temp, check);
858 Cell::VisitGridObjects(me, searcher, 150.0f);
859
860 _aliveTrash.clear();
861 for (std::list<Creature*>::iterator itr = temp.begin(); itr != temp.end(); ++itr)
862 if ((*itr)->GetHomePosition().GetPositionY() > minY)
863 _aliveTrash.insert((*itr)->GetGUID());
864 }
865 }

867 void DamageTaken(Unit*, uint32& damage, DamageEffectType, SpellSchoolMask) override
868 {
869 if (HealthBelowPct(10))
870 {
871 if (!_didUnderTenPercentText)
872 {
873 _didUnderTenPercentText = true;
874 if (me->GetVictim() && me->GetVictim()->GetEntry() == NPC_SISTER_SVALNA)
875 Talk(SAY_CROK_WEAKENING_SVALNA);
876 else
877 Talk(SAY_CROK_WEAKENING_GAUNTLET);
878 }
879
880 damage = 0;
881 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_ICEBOUND_ARMOR, true);
882 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_HEALTH_CHECK, 1000);
883 }
884 }

886 void UpdateEscortAI(uint32 /*diff*/) override {}
887
888 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
889 {
890 npc_escortAI::UpdateAI(diff);
891
892 //Position pos = me->GetHomePosition();
893 if (!me->isActiveObject()/* && me->GetExactDist(&pos) < 5.0f*/) // during event
894 return;
895
896 if (_wipeCheckTimer <= diff)
897 {
898 _wipeCheckTimer = 3000;
899
900 Player* player = nullptr;
901 Acore::AnyPlayerInObjectRangeCheck check(me, 140.0f);
902 Acore::PlayerSearcher<Acore::AnyPlayerInObjectRangeCheck> searcher(me, player, check);
903 Cell::VisitWorldObjects(me, searcher, 140.0f);
904 // wipe
905 if (!player || me->GetExactDist(4357.0f, 2606.0f, 350.0f) > 125.0f)
906 {
907 //Talk(SAY_CROK_DEATH);
908 FrostwingGauntletRespawner respawner;
909 Acore::CreatureWorker<FrostwingGauntletRespawner> worker(me, respawner);
910 Cell::VisitGridObjects(me, worker, 333.0f);
911 return;
912 }
913 }
914 else
915 _wipeCheckTimer -= diff;
916
917 UpdateVictim();
918
919 _events.Update(diff);
920
921 if (me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING))
922 return;
923
924 switch (_events.ExecuteEvent())
925 {
926 case EVENT_ARNATH_INTRO_2:
927 if (Creature* arnath = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_CAPTAIN_ARNATH)))
928 arnath->AI()->Talk(SAY_ARNATH_INTRO_2);
929 break;
930 case EVENT_CROK_INTRO_3:
931 Talk(SAY_CROK_INTRO_3);
932 break;
933 case EVENT_START_PATHING:
934 me->RemoveUnitFlag(UNIT_FLAG_NON_ATTACKABLE);
935 me->SetImmuneToAll(false);
936 Start(true, true);
937 break;
938 case EVENT_SCOURGE_STRIKE:
939 DoCastVictim(SPELL_SCOURGE_STRIKE);
940 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SCOURGE_STRIKE, urand(10000, 14000));
941 break;
942 case EVENT_DEATH_STRIKE:
943 if (HealthBelowPct(20))
944 DoCastVictim(SPELL_DEATH_STRIKE);
945 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DEATH_STRIKE, urand(5000, 10000));
946 break;
947 case EVENT_HEALTH_CHECK:
948 if (HealthAbovePct(25))
949 {
950 me->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_ICEBOUND_ARMOR);
951 _didUnderTenPercentText = false;
952 }
953 else
954 {
955 Unit::DealHeal(me, me, me->CountPctFromMaxHealth(3));
956 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_HEALTH_CHECK, 1000);
957 }
958 break;
959 default:
960 break;
961 }
962
963 DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
964 }
965
966 bool CanAIAttack(Unit const* target) const override
967 {
968 // do not see targets inside Frostwing Halls when we are not there
969 return target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER && (me->GetPositionY() > 2660.0f) == (target->GetPositionY() > 2660.0f) && target->GetEntry() != NPC_SINDRAGOSA;
970 }
971
972 private:
973 EventMap _events;
974 GuidSet _aliveTrash;
975 InstanceScript* _instance;
976 uint32 _currentWPid;
977 uint32 _wipeCheckTimer;
978 bool _handledWP4;
979 bool _isEventDone;
980 bool _didUnderTenPercentText;
981 };
982

984 {
985 return GetIcecrownCitadelAI<npc_crok_scourgebaneAI>(creature);
